== Akamaro k'igiti ==
Igiti gifite umumaro munini mu mibereho ya muntu ndestse n' ibindi binyabuzima bitandukanye biri ku isi, Igiti ni ubuturo rw' urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima bikirimo ari ibigaragara n'ibyo tutabonesha amaso, igiti gifasha mu kurwanya isuri, igiti cyera imbuto ziribwa, igiti gutanga igicucu ku myaka mu murima, igiti kifashishwa mu gushingirira indi myaka nk'ibishyimbo n'ibindi, igiti gitanga amavuta, igiti kandi gifasha mu gutanga umwuka duhumeka mwiza<ref>https://imvahonshya.co.rw/?p=4958</ref>.

